TOSSDR Installation instructions
--------------------------------
Author: Markus Becker
--------------------------------

# 1) install GNUradio r11020 from SVN (later versions might work)
#    according to its installation instructions

# 2) install the modified UCLA IEEE 802.15.4 SDR code in ucla/
#    according to the instructions

# 3) copy the make target, SDR components and hardware files into the
#    $TOSROOT with installIntoTree.sh:

chmod +x ./installIntoTree.sh
./installIntoTree.sh

# 4) go to the application directory you want to compile for the SDR
#    and compile it:

cd $(TOSROOT)/apps/test/TestAM/ make micaz sdr

# 5) run the application on the SDR:

cp $(TOSCONTRIB)/uob/tossdr/sdr2tos.py .
cp $(TOSCONTRIB)/uob/tossdr/sdr_handling.py .
python sdr2tos.py
